

Version 0.3 dependencies:

  Linux / Windows (tested on fedora 24)
  python3
  tkinter
  ping/ping6
  
To run: python3 __init__.py

Beware this code is not yet finished, 
some buttons/options won't work yet and it contains some unused boilercode.

Working (yet):
	ipv4 monitoring
	ipv4 scanning + import (presets/get hostnames/ping timeout/import selected don't work)
	load a backgroundimage/floorplans/googlemaps screenshot into the map
	save/load .nodes files to/from disk

Config: edit the nodes.ini file or any saved .nodes file with a texteditor. (utf-8 encoded)


